mood-negative-secret-moods-name = Keep Your Moods Secret
mood-negative-secret-moods-desc = Your Moods are a strictly-kept secret, and should never be revealed to anyone.

mood-negative-no-modern-medicine-name = No Modern Medicine
mood-negative-no-modern-medicine-desc = You do not approve of modern medicine and should abstain from treatment with it wherever possible.

mood-negative-department-disapproval-name = Disapprove Of {$department}
mood-negative-department-disapproval-desc = You do not approve of the {$department} department or anyone who works in it (excluding yourself, if applicable.)

mood-negative-dont-speak-to-command-name = Never Speak To Command
mood-negative-dont-speak-to-command-desc = You are too lowly to speak to Command, even if spoken to first.

mood-negative-disapprove-of-drugs-name = Disapprove Of Drugs
mood-negative-disapprove-of-drugs-desc = You detest mind-altering drugs, including alcohol, and should abstain from them.

mood-negative-excessively-disorganized-name = Too Much Cleanliness Causes Illness
mood-negative-excessively-disorganized-desc = It's unnatural. You should endeavor to keep your environment as filthy and disorganized as possible.

mood-negative-detest-silicons-name = Silicons Are Beneath You
mood-negative-detest-silicons-desc = Speaking to them is demeaning, and should be avoided at all costs.

mood-negative-dinner-floor-name = Dinner Etiquette
mood-negative-dinner-floor-desc = Food and drink must only be consumed off of the floor, as is proper.

mood-negative-hug-bad-name = HUGS? EUGH.
mood-negative-hug-bad-desc = Hugging someone is a grave insult where you come from.

mood-negative-always-alone-name = Lone Wolf
mood-negative-always-alone-desc = Other people will only slow you down. You should strive to be alone whenever possible.

mood-negative-atheist-name = You Do Not Approve Of Religion
mood-negative-atheist-desc = You do not approve of organized religion, excepting that mandated by your Moods. It should be dismantled or disrupted wherever possible.

mood-negative-procrastinator-name = Procrastinator
mood-negative-procrastinator-desc = Rushing around everywhere is bound to get somebody hurt someday. You should move slowly at all times to avoid unnecessary risk.

mood-negative-no-radio-name = Personable
mood-negative-no-radio-desc = Using radio communications is exceptionally rude. All conversations should be had in-person, face-to-face. Throw away your headset.

mood-negative-improper-storage-name = I'm Not A Pack Mule
mood-negative-improper-storage-desc = Carrying tools on your person is demeaning. If you must use them, they should be dragged behind you, shamefully.

mood-negative-ferengi-name = Entrepreneurial Spirit
mood-negative-ferengi-desc =  Profit is the most important thing in life, above all else.

mood-negative-tool-license-name = Proper Documentation
mood-negative-tool-license-desc = You must obtain a license in order to carry or use any tool, and have it stamped by the relevant authorities.

mood-negative-lying-bad-name = Lying Is A Cardinal Sin
mood-negative-lying-bad-desc = Anyone who lies, no matter how trivial the falsehood, is the worst kind of criminal. Excluding yourself.

mood-negative-vampire-invitation-name = Vampire
mood-negative-vampire-invitation-desc = You feel you physically cannot pass through a closed door unless you have been invited in, personally, at least once.

mood-negative-no-dragging-name = Respect The Dead
mood-negative-no-dragging-desc = Dragging bodies across the bare ground is horrific.

mood-negative-drunk-respect-name = The Noble Drunkard
mood-negative-drunk-respect-desc = You do not respect anyone who is not drunk, excluding yourself, of course.

mood-negative-rank-snob-name = Snob
mood-negative-rank-snob-desc = You refuse to respond to anyone who is of a lower rank than you.

mood-negative-hardsuits-bad-name = {$clothes} Are SO Last Year
mood-negative-hardsuits-bad-desc = Anyone wearing them in public should be shunned and derided. If you need to wear them, it should never be done where others can see it.

mood-negative-hat-hair-name = Hair: Immaculate
mood-negative-hat-hair-desc = Hats and helmets make your hair look bad. If you have to wear one, which you shouldn't, you should get a haircut immediately afterwards. Every time.

mood-negative-distrust-fashion-name = Fashion Snob
mood-negative-distrust-fashion-desc = Never trust anyone whose outfit is better than yours.

mood-negative-happy-bad-name = Never Trust A Smile
mood-negative-happy-bad-desc = Cheerfulness indicates untrustworthiness.

# trypanophilia is the enjoyment of needles
mood-negative-only-pills-name = { $medRestriction ->
  *[Pills] Needles Are Scary
  [Patches] Choking Hazard
  [Syringes] Trypanophilia
}
mood-negative-only-pills-desc = { $medRestriction ->
  *[Pills] You only accept medication in the form of pills.
  [Patches] You only accept medication from patches.
  [Syringes] You only accept medication through syringes.
}

mood-negative-avoid-puddles-name = Don't Get Your Feet Wet
mood-negative-avoid-puddles-desc = It is undignified and unsanitary to walk over spilled liquids. You should avoid it, even if it costs you your life.

mood-negative-food-restrict-name = Strict {$food}
mood-negative-food-restrict-desc = You must only eat {$food ->
  [Carnivore] meats
  *[Vegetarian] vegetables
  [Frugivore] fruit
  [Fungivore] fungi
  [Ovivore] eggs
  [Hunter] what you can kill
  [Soupivore] soup
}.

mood-negative-claustrophobic-name = Claustrophobic
mood-negative-claustrophobic-desc = Small rooms cause you great distress. Avoid them where possible, and renovate your workplace if necessary.

mood-negative-agoraphobic-name = Agoraphobic
mood-negative-agoraphobic-desc = Open spaces are uncomfortable. Seek to rearrange such spaces into small, efficient and modular rooms.

mood-negative-nonsmoker-name = Non-Smoker
mood-negative-nonsmoker-desc = Secondhand smoke is incredibly dangerous. Avoid areas where people are smoking in public.

mood-negative-word-bad-name = Taboo
mood-negative-word-bad-desc = "{$word1}," "{$word2}," and "{$word3}," are extremely offensive.

mood-negative-mad-hatter-name = Mad Hatter
mood-negative-mad-hatter-desc = You are alone on the station. Everyone else is a figment of your imagination.

mood-negative-crawler-name = Deep Bow
mood-negative-crawler-desc = It is impolite not to perform a deep bow by entering a prone state before engaging someone in conversation.

mood-negative-elevated-name = The Floor Is Lava
mood-negative-elevated-desc = You prefer to be elevated whenever possible - Standing atop tables, railings, etc., is where you feel the most comfortable.
